\displaystyle\implies i2z=\text{Log}\left(\frac{i\cos\theta}{1+\sin\theta}\right)
\displaystyle\implies2iz=\log\left(\frac{\cos\theta}{1+\sin\theta}\right)+i\dfrac\pi2+2n\pi i
